    <head><placeName key="PL000000008647">法音<ptr target="fn26"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A016016">曇勇</persName>尼<ptr target="fn27"/>傳第十四</head><p><anchor n="T.50.2063.0944b18"/><lb ed="T" n="0944b18"/><persName key="A016016">曇<ptr target="fn28"/>勇</persName>者，<persName key="A015902">曇簡</persName>尼之姊也。為性剛直，不隨物以<lb ed="T" n="0944b19"/>傾動，常以禪律為務，不以衣食經懷。憩<placeName key="PL000000008647">法音<lb ed="T" n="0944b20"/>精舍</placeName>，深悟無常，高崇我樂。以<date from-iso="0494-12-06" key="j19018301901897" to-iso="0495-02-11">建武元年</date>，隨<persName key="A015902">簡</persName><lb ed="T" n="0944b21"/><ptr target="fn29"/>同移<placeName key="PL000000000147">白山</placeName>。<date key="j19041261904126" when-iso="0501-03-21">永元三年二月十五日</date>夜，積薪自<lb ed="T" n="0944b22"/>燒，以身供養。當時聞見，咸發道心，共聚遺燼，<lb ed="T" n="0944b23"/>以立墳剎云。</p>
    
